 to our measurements are negligible. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2010 12:56:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2010 17:45:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2010 17:28:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
